类 ProofData

  • java.lang.Object
    • fchen.ProofData

  • public class ProofData
extends java.lang.Object
    It encapsulates the data returned by the cloud. Because of the privacy concern, this data structure is modified in this case. Now the query file name is a series MACs of all possible file names.

    Chen, Fei
